073500     ELSE
073600             PERFORM 070-E-REJ-CHAS  THRU    070-S-REJ-CHAS.
073700
073800
073900     IF      CH-NOTFOUND             =       "S"
074000             GO                      TO      040-S-RENAJUD.
074100
074200
074300     COMPUTE AC-QTD-RESTR  =  REJ-QTD-RESTR-AT + REJ-QTD-RESTR-IN.
074400
074500
074600     PERFORM 050-E-RESTR-REJ         THRU    050-S-RESTR-REJ
074700             VARYING IX1             FROM    1   BY  1
074800             UNTIL   IX1             >       4             OR
074900                     IX1             >       AC-QTD-RESTR  OR
075000                     CH-NOTFOUND     =       "S".
075100
075200
075300
075400
075500
075600 040-S-RENAJUD.
075700     EXIT.
