077300
077400
077500     PERFORM 050-E-RESTR-REJ         THRU    050-S-RESTR-REJ
077600             VARYING IX1             FROM    1   BY  1
077700             UNTIL   IX1             >       4             OR
077800                     IX1             >       AC-QTD-RESTR  OR
077900                     CH-NOTFOUND     =       "S".
078000
